{"tid":978004,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"（泰拳）召集有興趣一齊玩","createTime":"2019-01-11T14:57:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T03:53:09.000Z","uid":82070,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6f956786d23c5c6ece6cb089145c6dbf88e49b","tid":978004,"uid":82070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:57:47.000Z","msg":"［泰拳group］<br />\n<br />\n前排成日碌連登，都唔覺有人搞泰拳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦見到有巴絲打問過有無人打，而自己堅好想打<br />\n但自己一個又真係唔太夠膽，總係覺得唔自在&hellip;<br />\n聽講出面啲拳館有啲好雜，有啲又好貴，有啲仲會教錯姿勢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想揾一啲讀緊大專嘅一齊玩，若果有人一齊玩，我再問下邊一間較好<br />\n<br />\n歡迎有興趣嘅巴絲填以下Google Form，減肥又好，識多班朋友都好，發泄下又得，之後我會再聯絡大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScIobjKq105__1FfNFhIYywDVaW3TCqwFCQzUMTrzFhQJNzxw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScIobjKq105__1FfNFhIYywDVaW3TCqwFCQzUMTrzFhQJNzxw%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=NgKjo4LBFeldeS%2B0H1Leq10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=21e0394f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScIobjKq105__1FfNFhIYywDVaW3TCqwFCQzUMTrzFhQJNzxw/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：唔係中上男神<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f57e9a1ef699f669a95cbffd2770c1c363d7ef72","tid":978004,"uid":29702,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T14:59:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d63882c29476e02a897f33112191d1518b8a4a98","tid":978004,"uid":223084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-11T15:06:11.000Z","msg":"幾錢，以前想學但冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試堂都百幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"576325656611aad02828926bd